            "message": "좋습니다! 'book a table'도 맞는 표현이지만, 'make a reservation'이 더 formal합니다.",
            "points": 8,
            "suggestion": "I'd like to make a reservation, please."
          },
          "nextNodeId": "host-2a"
        },
        {
          "id": "opt-1c",
